Test       : XC Functionals
Programs   : octopus; octopus_mpi
TestGroups : short-run
Enabled    : Yes

Input: 03-xc.01-gs.inp
match ; Hartree-Fock energy                    ; GREP(static/info, 'Total       =', 20)   ; -0.57266977
match ; Hartree-Fock eigenvalue up             ; GREP(static/info, '  1   up', 13) ;  -1.269867
match ; Hartree-Fock eigenvalue dn             ; GREP(static/info, '  1   dn', 13) ;  -0.537714

Input: 03-xc.lda_x.inp
match ; LDA exchange                           ; GREP(out, 'Exchange    =', 20) ; -0.33035205

